QuestData.Title: Gods and Monsters
QuestData.Description: Dear $p,$b$bIs it true that the mogu are really connected to the titans? I find this very hard to believe. But looking over your research, some of the truth about the mogu begins to take shape.$b$bIf you visit us at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms we can add this contribution to your personal collection.$b$bThank you for your diligence!$b$bSincerely,$b$bLorewalker Cho
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Gods and Monsters to Lorewalker Cho.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Lorewalker Cho at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
